body:
Hi Everyone,
 This is a fun forum game that I would like to introduce. I call it the nickname game. Basically how U play is by giving the player above U a nickname. For ex: I give Matt_Skywalker30 the nickname Hacker. Also I asked Matt_Skywalker30 to use this as an example and he said it is okay
Rules:
1: No spamming this topic.
2: No rude/offensive nicknames
3: Have fun!
